name: Threat Intel for AWS - Optimized
description: The Sumo Logic Threat Intel for AWS App helps you identify security threats by correlating daily updated threat definitions from CrowdStrike against your log data using the threat lookup service. This App provides pre built dashboards and queries to analyze threats in your AWS CloudTrail, Amazon VPC Flow Logs, and AWS Elastic Load Balancing Classic logs.

children.name: Threat Intel for AWS - AWS CloudTrail - Optimized

panels.name: Threats Over Time by Result
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_cloudtrail
| timeslice 1h
| sum(_count) by _timeslice, result
| transpose row _timeslice column result

panels.name: Threats By Actor
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_cloudtrail
| sum(_count) by actor

panels.name: Threats by Events and IP
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_cloudtrail
| sum(_count) by  src_ip, event_name
| transpose row src_ip column event_name

panels.name: Threats by Geo Location
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_cloudtrail
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = src_ip
| sum(_count) by latitude, longitude, label_name,threat_last_updated

panels.name: Threats by Events and Result
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_cloudtrail
| sum(_count) by event_name, result
| transpose row event_name column result

panels.name: Threats Associated with CloudTrail Events
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_cloudtrail
| sum(_count) by event_time, src_user,src_ip,event_name, aws_region , result , malicious_confidence, label_name,  threat_malware_families,threat_last_updated

children.name: Threat Intel for AWS - AWS Elastic Load Balancing - Application - Optimized

panels.name: Threats Associated with  Client IP
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_alb
| sum(_count) by elb_resource, elb_status_code, domain, client_ip, client_port , target_ip, target_port, malicious_confidence, label_name,  threat_malware_families,threat_last_updated
| fields - _sum

panels.name: Threats Associated with Domain
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_alb
| sum(_count) by elb_resource, elb_status_code, domain, client_ip, client_port , target_ip, target_port, malicious_confidence, label_name,  threat_malware_families,threat_last_updated
| fields - _sum

panels.name: Client IP Threats by Geo Location
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_alb
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = client_ip
| sum(_count) by latitude, longitude, label_name,threat_last_updated

panels.name: Client IP Threats by Actor
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_alb
| sum(_count) by actor

panels.name: Client IP Threats Over Time by ELB Resource
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_alb
| timeslice 1h
| sum(_count) by _timeslice, elb_resource
| transpose row _timeslice column elb_resource

panels.name: Client IP Threats by ELB Server
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_alb
| sum(_count) by client_ip, elb_resource
| transpose row client_ip column elb_resource

children.name: Threat Intel for AWS - Amazon VPC Flow Logs - Optimized

panels.name: Total Threats
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_vpc
| sum(_count) as threats

panels.name: Geo Location of Threats with Rejected Flow Logs
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_vpc
| where action matches "REJECT"
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = src_ip
| sum(_count) by latitude, longitude, label_name,threat_last_updated

panels.name: Geo Location of Threats with Accepted Flow Logs
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_vpc
| where action matches "ACCEPT"
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = src_ip
| sum(_count) by latitude, longitude, label_name,threat_last_updated

panels.name: High Malicious Confidence Threats
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_vpc
| where malicious_confidence matches "high"
| sum(_count) as threats

panels.name: Threats Associated with Rejected Flow Logs
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_vpc
| where action matches "REJECT"
| concat ( src_ip," : ", src_port) as src
| concat ( dest_ip," : ", dest_port) as dest
| sum(_count) by interfaceID, accountID, src, dest, Protocol, malicious_confidence, label_name,  threat_malware_families,threat_last_updated

panels.name: Threats Associated with Accepted Flow Logs
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_vpc
| where action matches "ACCEPT"
| concat ( src_ip," : ", src_port) as src
| concat ( dest_ip," : ", dest_port) as dest
| sum(_count) by interfaceID, accountID, src, dest, Protocol, malicious_confidence, label_name,  threat_malware_families,threat_last_updated

panels.name: Threat Breakdown
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_vpc
| concat ( src_ip," : ", src_port) as src
| concat ( dest_ip," : ", dest_port) as dest
| sum(_count) by actor, Action

panels.name: Top 10 Threat Sources by Action
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_vpc
| concat ( src_ip," : ", src_port) as src
| concat ( dest_ip," : ", dest_port) as dest
| sum(_count) as threats by src_ip,Action
| top 10 src_ip, Action by threats

panels.name: Threats Over Time by Action
panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_vpc
| timeslice 1h
| sum(_count) by _timeslice, Action
| transpose row _timeslice column Action

panels.queryString:
_view=threat_intel_cloudtrail
| timeslice 15m
| sum(_count) as threats by _timeslice
| outlier threats

panels.name: Scanned Events by Source Category
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = *cloudtrail* or _sourceCategory = *vpc*  or _sourceCategory = *alb* 
| count as events by _sourceCategory

children.name: Threats Associated with Accepted VPC Traffic Flow - Optimized
children.searchQuery:
_view=threat_intel_vpc
| where action="ACCEPT"
//| where malicious_confidence matches "high"
| concat ( src_ip," : ", src_port) as src
| concat ( dest_ip," : ", dest_port) as dest
| sum(_count) as threats by interfaceID, accountID, src, dest, Protocol, malicious_confidence, label_name,  threat_malware_families,threat_last_updated
| sort by threats

children.name: Threats Associated with CloudTrail Events - Optimized
children.searchQuery:
_view=threat_intel_cloudtrail
//| where malicious_confidence matches "high"
| sum(_count) as threats by event_time, src_user,src_ip,event_name, aws_region , result , malicious_confidence, label_name,  threat_malware_families,threat_last_updated
| sort by threats

children.name: Threats Associated with requesting Client - ELB - Optimized
children.searchQuery:
_view=threat_intel_alb
| sum(_count) as threats by elb_resource, elb_status_code, domain, client_ip, client_port, target_ip, target_port, malicious_confidence, label_name,  threat_malware_families,threat_last_updated
| fields - threats
